					JOHANA
		Do you ever sometimes just stop and
		think how sweet life can be?

A beat.

					JACQUES
		... Sure.

JOHANA wants to say something.

					JOHANA
		... When you dive... with that
		machine... What does it feel like?

					JACQUES
